        <updateDate>2015-01-09T20:05:48Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Responsible Skies Act of 2014 - Amends the FAA Modernization and Reform Act of 2012 to require the Secretary of Transportation (DOT) to prohibit the operator of an unmanned recreational aircraft (drone) from flying it:</p> <ul> <li>above 400 feet and within 5 miles of the perimeter of a commercial airport, or</li> <li>where it may be seen from the airport's perimeter.</li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
